{"tid":1480222,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"唔該紅土手足嗌「光復紅土，還我淨土」","createTime":"2019-08-17T08:10:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T08:54:45.000Z","uid":39752,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d3a24db88b3f52cdd08ceffc08c80e3984ce3712","tid":1480222,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T08:10:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復紅土，還我淨土<br />\n光復紅土，還我淨土<br />\n光復紅土，還我淨土</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n本來搞今次遊行係打算主打民生議題<br />\n唔介意大家嗌五大訴求同光復香港，但係紅土口號無人嗌就過份咗少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望大家好似屯公嗰次咁幫手嗌一嗌地區口號<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e62f59c863b207aaea7bb011a06e434fd096707b","tid":1480222,"uid":200136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T08:10:32.000Z","msg":"紅土人push"},{"pid":"08384ea6c1fea07a3c93e69a05570b7fcb042c98","tid":1480222,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T08:10:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12dc02ac90b837a6f6674ad9d931a0c7745fbc72","tid":1480222,"uid":200136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T08:11:05.000Z","msg":"對啊"},{"pid":"248da0e4d21b903b75c2b3ba43eff94206366e1e","tid":1480222,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T08:12:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"495718ff8d3863d74c56ec106e747aad2dda8596","tid":1480222,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T08:13:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e81004b6c9f30a5f12e6c4d10c441e6d7d041e6","tid":1480222,"uid":200136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T08:14:02.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3421c86c4c1837932d29df70b32f13dfe21be853","tid":1480222,"uid":79046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T08:14:50.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，借一借位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【和理非升級】８２３人鏈籌備召集！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1480152\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1480152</a>"},{"pid":"85ceec3c3b634cb998ae6e8ae6a06217de1b8747","tid":1480222,"uid":39752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T08:15:15.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復紅土 還我靜土<br />\n紅土朱古力，專呃 china pig<br />\n紅土朱古力，專呃中國的<br />\n大陸團，冇時完！<br />\n大陸遊客日日嚟 紅土街坊無埞企<br />\n紅土只是生活區 遊客不要一堆堆<br />\n紅土日日亂 踢走大陸團<br />\n遊客塞到大門口 居民落街無路行</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n俾負皮嗰隻食屎狗快啲入返你老母個西度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6d8ec8a51b354551e2301138e008f89e194469a","tid":1480222,"uid":268160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T08:15:36.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f56d30f81c60ab31af3671759553d0f07f990604","tid":1480222,"uid":279963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T08:15:56.000Z","msg":"我而家整理緊資料，希望由1982年中英談判開始，<br />\n講到今日點解我地要企出來以武力手段爭取民主<br />\n<br />\n要完成呢個list需要大家一齊去搵資料，<br />\n因為我一個人絕對冇辦法完成。<br />\n當中包括<br />\n1。一條相關新聞/wiki<br />\n2。一張相關照片<br />\n3。中文及/或英文簡介<br />\n<br />\n希望各位可以幫下我手入<br />\n去呢個google sheet入面將呢個list完成:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1c39ls77nUy_Vrr1mhIbduxIEpa7PkKRz2jZYI8hsJOA/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1c39ls77nUy_Vrr1mhIbduxIEpa7PkKRz2jZYI8hsJOA%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=9fV5YN%2BdLeg0vJDpI0pnmluXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=92284f3f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1c39ls77nUy_Vrr1mhIbduxIEpa7PkKRz2jZYI8hsJOA/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n切記，唔好整得太長，<br />\n唔好芝麻綠豆小事都擺入去<br />\n感謝各位幫忙<br />\n<br />\n我會將呢個list整成一套MEME<br />\n例子如下：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0BKFO0F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0BKFO0F.jpg&h=f2c7434b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n目前個list有：<br />\n1979 香港前途問題<br />\n1984 中英談判<br />\n1984 中英聯合聲明<br />\n1988 八八直選<br />\n1989 天安門事件<br />\n1989 天安門事件<br />\n1989 天安門事件<br />\n1991 九一直選<br />\n1992 彭定康港督<br />\n1995 臨時立法會<br />\n1996 移民潮<br />\n1997 中國收回香港<br />\n1997 建華亂港<br />\n1997 禽流感<br />\n1998 胡仙案<br />\n1998 亞洲金融風暴<br />\n1999 居港權釋法<br />\n1999 市政局解散<br />\n2002 高官問責制<br />\n2003 SARS<br />\n2003 廿三條立法<br />\n2003 偷步買車<br />\n2003 七一遊行<br />\n <br />\n2003 自由行政策<br />\n2004 釋法否決07/08雙普選<br />\n2005 領匯<br />\n2005 老董腳痛落台<br />\n2006 天星保育<br />\n2007 皇后保育<br />\n2008 社民連三子<br />\n2010 反高鐵<br />\n2010 五區公投<br />\n2010 馬尼拉人質事件<br />\n2011 民主黨接受政改方案<br />\n2012 流浮山飯局<br />\n2012 特首梁振英689票<br />\n2012 國民教育<br />\n2013 HKTV不獲發牌<br />\n2014 831框架<br />\n2014 戴耀庭提議佔領中環<br />\n2014 雨傘革命<br />\n2014 暗角七警<br />\n2015 否決政改<br />\n2016 旺角魚蛋革命<br />\n2017 反一地兩檢<br />\n2018 UGL 50M 事件放生"},{"pid":"7f5b872e74dd154ee67fd742f27e4f7a85a0acf2","tid":1480222,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T08:17:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcfdf49c97c3fd17450cc5087d07639ee6011f59","tid":1480222,"uid":271199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T08:18:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"020b69af3c4a8e2bb9b2eecba5e5d3cf1f33fec5","tid":1480222,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T08:24:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3f3e6657f0e089e63442a580e06d916d0e1109e","tid":1480222,"uid":140924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T08:24:59.000Z","msg":"推到現場手足睇到"},{"pid":"a5daa605b3b7f8f6e8444d5e3e616061b7